#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_2
msgid ""
"<strong>The Masterclass Experience:</strong>\n"
"This hands-on training takes place in a creative studio environment where theory meets practice. You'll analyze successful case studies, participate in platform-specific breakout sessions, and develop a customized influencer strategy blueprint for your brand. Our expert instructors bring insights from managing influencer campaigns across diverse industries and budget levels."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Masterclass-oplevelsen:</strong>\n"
"Denne praktiske træning foregår i et kreativt studiemiljø, hvor teori møder "
"praksis. Du vil analysere succesfulde casestudier, deltage i "
"platformspecifikke breakout-sessioner og udvikle en skræddersyet influencer-"
"strategi for dit brand. Vores ekspertinstruktører deler deres erfaringer med "
"at styre influencer-kampagner på tværs af forskellige brancher og "
"budgetniveauer."

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_4
msgid ""
"<strong>The Showcase Experience:</strong>\n"
"Hosted in an elegant setting, the Results Showcase combines insightful presentations with interactive discussions. We transform complex data into clear visualizations that tell the story of your marketing performance. The event culminates in a collaborative planning session where we identify key initiatives for the coming quarter."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Showcase-oplevelsen:</strong>\n"
"Præsentation af markedsføringsresultater, der finder sted i elegante "
"omgivelser, kombinerer indsigtsfulde oplæg med interaktive diskussioner. Vi "
"omsætter komplekse data til overskuelige visualiseringer, der tydeligt viser "
"jeres marketingresultater. Arrangementet afsluttes med et fælles "
"planlægningsmøde, hvor de vigtigste initiativer for det kommende kvartal "
"fastlægges."

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:sale.order.template,note:marketing_agency.sale_order_template_4
msgid "<strong>Timeline:</strong> 6-8 weeks from project kickoff to launch"
msgstr "<strong>Tidsplan:</strong> 6-8 uger fra projektstart til lancering"

